# Group-Study-Application
You're no longer alone.
REVE – Study Group Application
A modern microservices-based platform for students to study together, track progress, and collaborate.
This project includes:
Frontend: React + TypeScript + TailwindCSS
Backend (Microservices): Node.js + Express + PostgreSQL + Redis
API Gateway: Reverse proxy for routing requests
Authentication: JWT-based login/signup, email verification, password reset
 Architecture Overview
Frontend (React + TS)
        │
        ▼
  API Gateway (8080)
        │
  ┌───────────────┬────────────────┬──────────────────┐
  ▼               ▼                ▼                  ▼
Auth Service   User Service   Admin Service     Other Services...
PostgreSQL     PostgreSQL       PostgreSQL
Redis Cache
Frontend sends ALL requests only to API Gateway
Gateway routes requests to the appropriate microservice
Microservices communicate with DBs independently

